{"tid":1722063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真係被騎劫嘅話唔好忍，忍就輸一世","createTime":"2019-11-14T21:40:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T23:07:44.000Z","uid":35604,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f15422640e641a1fcc950e4fa624e2eb18a02522","tid":1722063,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:40:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/qs4bmy4/CAA96-CA4-158-A-4-F85-817-C-697-ACE23992-B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fqs4bmy4%2FCAA96-CA4-158-A-4-F85-817-C-697-ACE23992-B.jpg&h=0a78f83a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/DKT6Dz5/ADFF1-AF1-21-CB-4036-8467-04-E40316-CE17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FDKT6Dz5%2FADFF1-AF1-21-CB-4036-8467-04-E40316-CE17.jpg&h=58b1f2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係想割<br />\n都唔可以一句我係手足就拎人地學生守中大心血嚟玩<br />\n唔好咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得佔中<br />\n被騎劫拆路障開路<br />\n被騎劫大台<br />\n辛苦用盡力換嚟比人當玩具咁撚<br />\n係杞人憂天架喇<br />\n但係情況真係太似<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/983060081720923/?v=983060081720923\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsocrec%2Fvideos%2F983060081720923%2F%3Fv%3D983060081720923&d=KYS9j8ljDCWJrVyje8%2BOjcorGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=89129f36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/socrec/videos/983060081720923/?v=983060081720923</a>"},{"pid":"47b525cc2d25f415bab91a134be01254903e52cf","tid":1722063,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:42:29.000Z","msg":"真係望見都PTSD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n隨便負皮啦"},{"pid":"397bb0aa0d7b8815a5d61748fe8c0f56a7e28782","tid":1722063,"uid":35604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T21:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face